@fourfa: Solar panel and vector attach node are easy fixes, I have my suspicions about what's going on with the R-71 cockpit, but it's been due for a remodel for a while now so it'll get fixed one way or the other.

@Beetlecat: Correct:  
![W3xdUDe.png](http://i.imgur.com/W3xdUDe.png)  

if stacking chines they'll have to be placed in 1x symmetry or with radial symmetry instead of mirror symmetry. Probably shouldn't be an issue with normal chine usage, wing root chines, if being used as wing roots will need to be placed without using stack attach nodes.

