@JayPee: I honestly don't remember. By mistake, probably. I've reupped a fixed version of 1.7.35 that fixes this.  

@MannaroThePatient; Banshee fans have always used <abbr title="Liquid Fuel">LF</abbr>/O by default. The Electric or <abbr title="Liquid Fuel">LF</abbr>/Air fuel modes for the Banshee are provided via <abbr title="Module Manager (mod)">MM</abbr> patches found in the Extras folder.

